Lovely" is a song by Canadian singer Justin Bieber, featuring American singer-songwriter Billie Eilish. It was released as a single in 2018 and received positive feedback from audiences and critics alike for its mellow and intimate sound, as well as for the strong vocal performances by both Bieber and Eilish. The song has been praised for its simple yet effective production and lyrics, and for the way it showcases the emotions and feelings of love and affection. It has become a fan favorite and continues to be widely streamed and played on various music platforms.
